main event: An unidentified flying object was observed in California between 2005 and 2020, classified after analysis as likely a natural phenomenon such as a meteorite or missile trail.
interesting points: The observation lasted from 2005 to 2020 but was of short duration,The object was streak-like in appearance and light in color,No photographs or physical evidence were collected,The conclusion categorized the sighting as a natural phenomenon,There were multiple sightings of the object by different observers.
